name: ibex
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "ibex" %}
{% set version = "0.1.3" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 989db0004432c50e237c34d99912d10c00552e2bb57e162de11799378d9bd40e

build:
  noarch: python
  number: 0
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . --no-deps --ignore-installed --no-cache-dir -vvv"

requirements:
  host:
    - python >=3.5
    - pip
  run:
    - python >=3.5
    - six
    - numpy
    - scipy
    - scikit-learn
    - pandas

test:
  imports:
    - ibex
    - ibex.sklearn

about:
  home: https://github.com/atavory/ibex
  license: BSD-3-Clause
  license_family: BSD
  # PR to add license_file to src distribution:  https://github.com/atavory/ibex/pull/32
  license_file: LICENSE.txt
  summary: 'Pandas Adapters For Scikit-Learn'
  doc_url: https://atavory.github.io/ibex/

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - dhirschfeld
